summary: This is a very basic follower mod I made for my brother for his birthday. Just wanted to put it somewhere, don't pay it any attention.
descriptionHtml:
Elanna the Healer is a powerful breton mage. She is skilled in conjuration mostly. 

She is found hanging out in Arcadia's Cauldron in Whiterun. 

Elanna has nothing really special, just basic dialogue and clothing. She is a blank page for new adventures!
author: BSNsolstice
